### Git command usage
**Configure**  
 # git config --global user.name "John Doe"  
 # git config --global user.email johndoe@example.com  
 # git config -l  
**Initializing a new repository**  
 # git init  
**Check current status**  
 # git status  
**Committing changes**  
 # git add -A  
 # git commit -m "description"